{"tid":2500862,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方機場反恐演習　指防範本土恐怖主義死灰復燃","createTime":"2021-04-23T03:24:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T03:51:16.000Z","uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2bd4f3043fc2efefba56c99350e5c005b585f3d7","tid":2500862,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:24:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=432159\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D432159&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrX%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=3c23641e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D432159&h=7ae58044\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=432159</a><br />\n<br />\n 警方指，本港的恐襲威脅維持在中度，即有可能但沒有線報顯示會成為恐襲目標，但要防範本土恐怖主義死灰復燃。<br />\n<br />\n跨部門反恐專責組處理高級警司梁偉基：「本港自從2019年下半年開始，面對本土恐怖主義冒起的威脅，近期社會形勢似乎逐漸恢復穩定，但香港與其他海外國家或地區一樣，都要提防本土恐怖主義隨時死灰復燃。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d3e26a7c490854869d4e8c851a93a566e9dae0","tid":2500862,"uid":53062,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:25:48.000Z","msg":"警方應該真係好想香港有恐怖分子，愈亂愈多水搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112e030e89389ee361b0fffe42bc73a9ca85c2c7","tid":2500862,"uid":54593,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:29:45.000Z","msg":"1967就是共黨恐怖主義"},{"pid":"fef1869a8b8620cf5c8757b5142cdde1bb99c387","tid":2500862,"uid":345502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91d3e26a7c490854869d4e8c851a93a566e9dae0","tid":2500862,"uid":53062,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:25:48.000Z","msg":"警方應該真係好想香港有恐怖分子，愈亂愈多水搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:30:07.000Z","msg":"咩想? 香